Qupzilla (Qt5 Qwebengine browser). you don't need """""Tor browser""""", you just need this in your `/etc/tor/torrc`

    CookieAuthentication 1
    CookieAuthFileGroupReadable 1
    CookieAuthFile /var/lib/tor-auth/control_auth_cookie
    ControlPort 9051
